✨ GIVEAWAY TIME! ✨
I’ve partnered with @meshki in collab with their recent #MESHKIEnchantedGarden collection, where one lucky follower will WIN a Bottega Veneta bag! 👜
Prize includes:
🤍 1 x Bottega Veneta Chain Cassette Shoulder Bag
To enter:
1. Like this post
2. Tag your friends (can enter multiple times with a new comment)
3. Make sure you and all your besties are following @amandakhamkaew + @meshki 
4. BONUS ENTRY: Share this competition post to your stories & tag @amandakhamkaew + @meshki 
5. BONUS ENTRY x 2: Comment on @meshki most recent posts saying why you want to win
#MESHKIEnchantedGarden
Comp is open worldwide and ends 31st July. Goodluck babes! Exclusive to www.meshki.com.au
